people in the series.

00:14:04.920 --> 00:14:08.320
Because that is less likely
to becoming from

00:14:08.320 --> 00:14:11.360
industrialization in general and
more likely to be coming

00:14:11.360 --> 00:14:13.390
from the fact that
you've seen them.

00:14:13.390 --> 00:14:16.056
But that's very well taken.

00:14:16.056 --> 00:14:19.014
AUDIENCE: Did they
observe a lag?

00:14:19.014 --> 00:14:22.465
Like the introduction of the
TV show and the shift in

00:14:22.465 --> 00:14:22.970
