when the TV came, and whose

00:14:45.750 --> 00:14:48.860
views were shaped by this.

00:14:48.860 --> 00:14:52.550
And this is exactly this timing
that helps, to some

00:14:52.550 --> 00:14:56.220
extent, discriminate between
the idea that the TV caused

00:14:56.220 --> 00:14:59.520
the reduction of the fertility
and your perfectly legitimate

00:14:59.520 --> 00:15:02.990
point that, in fact, in part
it could also be that TV is

00:15:02.990 --> 00:15:06.112
