but, in practice, the teachers

00:21:09.300 --> 00:21:11.630
are very shy about talking
about HIV.

00:21:11.630 --> 00:21:14.620
They don't want to be branded
as an HIV teacher.

00:21:14.620 --> 00:21:17.280
People are still pretty prudish
about the whole thing.

00:21:17.280 --> 00:21:21.320
So teachers won't do anything
about HIV AIDS prevention

00:21:21.320 --> 00:21:23.640
