00:30:42.340 --> 00:30:45.690
Basically, you can have
two kinds of sex.

00:30:45.690 --> 00:30:47.180
You can have casual sex.

00:30:47.180 --> 00:30:50.810
And you can have sex with
a regular partner.

00:30:50.810 --> 00:30:53.100
And then you can choose whether
