are pregnant.

00:32:09.310 --> 00:32:13.380
When this was happening, it was
the end of your schooling

00:32:13.380 --> 00:32:16.120
if you had a child.

00:32:16.120 --> 00:32:18.860
So the cost of the pregnancy is
that you're losing a chance

00:32:18.860 --> 00:32:22.660
to further your education
if you wanted to.

00:32:22.660 --> 00:32:25.690
So that's kind of the parameter
of what's happening.

00:32:25.690 --> 00:32:28.545
Now we have the girls, and
they are thinking, well.

00:32:28.545 --> 00:32:31.770
And of course, people like
to have sex, girls, too.

00:32:31.770 --> 00:32:35.050
So they are like weighing,
like, what should I do?

00:32:35.050 --> 00:32:37.140
How much sex should I have?

00:32:37.140 --> 00:32:39.700
Should I use contraception?

00:32:39.700 --> 00:32:47.740
And should I have a regular
partner that

00:32:47.740 --> 00:32:51.190
might lead to a marriage?

00:32:51.190 --> 00:32:53.750
Or should I have casual partners
that are not going to

00:32:53.750 --> 00:32:55.530
lead to marriage?

00:32:55.530 --> 00:32:59.770
And what the teacher training
program is telling them, if

00:32:59.770 --> 00:33:02.800
you have casual sex, you're
very, very, very

00:33:02.800 --> 00:33:04.040
likely to get an STD.

00:33:04.040 --> 00:33:07.130
It does change their probability
that they might

00:33:07.130 --> 00:33:09.000
get an STD.

00:33:09.000 --> 00:33:11.110
But if you have sex within
marriage, you're safe.

00:33:11.110 --> 00:33:13.670
You're fine.

00:33:13.670 --> 00:33:16.140
In fact, it might do the two
things at the same time.

00:33:16.140 --> 00:33:19.810
Maybe, girls have not realized
the difference between casual

00:33:19.810 --> 00:33:21.090
sex and married sex.

00:33:21.090 --> 00:33:23.110
But after the teacher training
program, they think married

00:33:23.110 --> 00:33:24.390
sex is very safe.

00:33:24.390 --> 00:33:27.330
And they think that casual
sex is very risky.

00:33:27.330 --> 00:33:29.760
And the truth is that married
sex is not necessarily that

00:33:29.760 --> 00:33:33.320
safe, because the candidate
for marriage, for a young

00:33:33.320 --> 00:33:36.780
girl, is usually not a young
boy, who would be unable to

00:33:36.780 --> 00:33:37.570
support a child.

00:33:37.570 --> 00:33:40.210
It's usually an older man,
what they call a "sugar

00:33:40.210 --> 00:33:45.630
daddy", who is able to provide
for the girl and then provide

00:33:45.630 --> 00:33:46.700
for the child.

00:33:46.700 --> 00:33:49.690
And the girls are convinced that
the "sugar daddies" are

00:33:49.690 --> 00:33:52.540
faithful to themselves
and their wives.

00:33:52.540 --> 00:33:54.600
But that might not
be entirely true.

00:33:54.600 --> 00:33:59.695
And so the actual risk of
infection in married sex and

00:33:59.695 --> 00:34:01.620
in casual sex might not
be that different.

00:34:04.742 --> 00:34:07.840
But when the teacher training
program arrived, they feel,

00:34:07.840 --> 00:34:10.350
oh, my god, I have to stop
having casual sex.

00:34:10.350 --> 00:34:12.920
That's very dangerous.

00:34:12.920 --> 00:34:15.929
Let me reduce, a little bit,
the sex I'm going to have.

00:34:15.929 --> 00:34:20.130
But let me also move towards
married sex.

00:34:20.130 --> 00:34:23.120
And by doing that, they're much
more likely to become

00:34:23.120 --> 00:34:26.650
pregnant, because, within
marriage, they think it's fine

00:34:26.650 --> 00:34:28.170
to have a kid.

00:34:28.170 --> 00:34:30.460
And also, they think that,
within marriage, they don't

00:34:30.460 --> 00:34:32.630
need to be protected as much.

00:34:32.630 --> 00:34:35.400
So for these two reasons, the
pregnancy rate will tend to

00:34:35.400 --> 00:34:36.900
increase if anything.

00:34:36.900 --> 00:34:39.409
On the other hand, they also
have less sex, so that

00:34:39.409 --> 00:34:42.830
