00:34:46.679 --> 00:34:48.429
instead of seeing a decrease.

00:34:48.429 --> 00:34:50.400
Because we see a reduction
in sex, but that's

00:34:50.400 --> 00:34:54.300
counterbalanced by a shift
towards this single

00:34:54.300 --> 00:34:55.330
relationship.

00:34:55.330 --> 00:34:57.560
And because the single
