00:35:35.610 --> 00:35:37.370
And that's going to reduce.

00:35:37.370 --> 00:35:38.850
So you're going to
dropout less.

00:35:38.850 --> 00:35:40.290
You're going to have
fewer kids.

00:35:40.290 --> 00:35:41.038
